## Historical lineage

Cuis Smalltalk descends from:

- **Squeak** contributors (1997–present)
- **Apple Computer, Inc.** — original Smalltalk-80 implementation (1985–1996)
- **Xerox Corp.** — Smalltalk-80 at Xerox PARC (1981–1982)
